sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>(Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe)
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as S3/GCS/Azure/PVC<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, etcd: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>ModelMesh: gRPC inference request<br/>8033/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Check model placement/routing<br/>2379/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model location & status
    ModelMesh->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC (localhost/UDS)
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
    ModelMesh-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client, etcd: Flow 2: REST Inference via OAuth
    Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS POST inference<br/>8443/TCP TLS, OAuth token
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate OAuth token<br/>SAR: get services in namespace
    OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: Forward (pre-authenticated)<br/>8008/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate REST→gRPC<br/>8033/TCP, Optional TLS (localhost)
    ModelMesh->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC (localhost/UDS)
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
    ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
    OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response

    Note over Controller, Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Predictor/InferenceService CRs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: New Predictor event
    Controller->>ModelMesh: registerModel / setVModel<br/>8033/TCP gRPC, Optional TLS
    ModelMesh->>etcd: Store model registration<br/>2379/TCP, credentials
    ModelMesh->>Puller: Trigger model download<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS, storage credentials
    Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller->>Runtime: Load model via adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC (localhost)
    Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Model loaded confirmation

    Note over Controller, K8sAPI: Flow 4: Controller Reconciliation
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read ServingRuntime spec<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: ServingRuntime definition
    Controller->>Controller: Render deployment template<br/>14-step transformation pipeline
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Service (headless)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update HPA (if enabled)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
